7432776069306294272,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/djsce_happy-to-inform-you-all-that-a-team-name-activity-7432776069306294272-YcrX,Happy to inform you all that a team (name: Innovate) of the following students of our Institute has secured the 1st position at "Decipher", a Case Study Competition organized by Atlas Skilltech… | Dwarkadas J. Sanghvi College of Engineering,https://in.linkedin.com/school/djsce/?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image,djsce,Happy to inform you all that a team (name: Innovate) of the following students of our Institute has secured the 1st position at "Decipher", a Case Study Competition organized by Atlas Skilltech University, Mumbai.,110,Happy to inform you all that a team (name: Innovate) of the following students of our Institute has secured the 1st position at "Decipher", a Case Study Competition organized by Atlas Skilltech University, Mumbai. Team members: Aryan Rathod (S.Y.-AI&DS), Prithviraj Shah (S.Y.-AI&DS) and Vrushti (T.Y.- AI&DS). Congratulations!!!! to all the team members and best wishes. 👏,post,2026-03-05T06:51:49.503Z,0,2026-02-26T13:18:29.208Z,Organization,6,0,Happy to inform you all that a team (name: Innovate) of the following students of our Institute has secured the 1st position at &quot;Decipher&quot;, a Case Study Competition organized by Atlas Skilltech University, Mumbai.<br/><br/>Team members:<br/>Aryan Rathod (S.Y.-AI&amp;DS), Prithviraj Shah (S.Y.-AI&amp;DS) and Vrushti (T.Y.- AI&amp;DS).<br/><br/><br/>Congratulations!!!! to all the team members and best wishes. 👏 ,17283,,500,,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4D0BAQFZRBOE0uG9Og/company-logo_100_100/company-logo_100_100/0/1675337351376/djsce_logo?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=4xq8Y27Y7GunrjHjN-SHwL7AtXsiAQUc9upExCd-oWQ
7427447635642351616,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/lakshitaa-chellaramani-68254224b_aivolution-hackathon-medianet-activity-7427447635642351616-i5r4,#aivolution #hackathon #medianet #codingdivas #womenintech #womenwhocode #buildboldly | Lakshitaa Chellaramani,https://in.linkedin.com/in/lakshitaa-chellaramani-68254224b?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image,lakshitaa-chellaramani-68254224b,🏆 1st Runner-Up at AiVolution Hackathon by Media.net — and we walked away with ₹1,50,000.,143,🏆 1st Runner-Up at AiVolution Hackathon by Media.net — and we walked away with ₹1,50,000. 💰 Team CodingDivas showed up, built something real, and delivered under pressure. Proud to have competed alongside my incredible teammate, Pinky Pamecha . We came in as final-year students, and we left as winners. What made this even sweeter? A Pre-Placement Interview with Media.net on top of the prize. 🎯 To every person who told me hackathons were just for fun, they can be. But they can also be the room where you prove what you're made of. This is just the beginning. 🚀 #AiVOLUTION #Hackathon #MediaNet #CodingDivas #WomenInTech #WomenWhoCode #BuildBoldly,post,2026-03-05T06:51:50.271Z,12,2026-02-11T20:25:11.619Z,Person,2,0,🏆 1st Runner-Up at AiVolution Hackathon by <a class="link" href="https://ae.linkedin.com/company/media.net?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Media.net</a> — and we walked away with ₹1,50,000. 💰<br/><br/>Team CodingDivas showed up, built something real, and delivered under pressure.<br/><br/>Proud to have competed alongside my incredible teammate, <a class="link" href="https://in.linkedin.com/in/pinkypamecha?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Pinky Pamecha</a>. We came in as final-year students, and we left as winners.<br/><br/>What made this even sweeter? A Pre-Placement Interview with <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=http%3A%2F%2FMedia%2Enet&amp;urlhash=CzNI&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" rel="nofollow" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Media.net</a> on top of the prize. 🎯<br/><br/>To every person who told me hackathons were just for fun, they can be. But they can also be the room where you prove what you&apos;re made of.<br/><br/>This is just the beginning. 🚀<br/><br/><a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Faivolution&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#AiVOLUTION</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fhackathon&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#Hackathon</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fmedianet&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#MediaNet</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fcodingdivas&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#CodingDivas</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwomenintech&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#WomenInTech</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwomenwhocode&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#WomenWhoCode</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fbuildboldly&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#BuildBoldly</a>,756,,500,,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D03AQH290Y7ejn6Ng/profile-displayphoto-scale_400_400/B4DZv9rL9HKoAg-/0/1769487517509?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=Eq5xxuyIuTMh8qt4FZ3GT_a9rV316idkPJf1XGQWRHI
7433700977142239232,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/dhravyashah_i-built-the-best-memory-for-voice-agents-activity-7433700977142239232-HChG,Voice AI with Super Memory Integration | Dhravya Shah posted on the topic | LinkedIn,https://www.linkedin.com/in/dhravyashah,dhravyashah,I built the best memory for voice agents while sponsoring @YCombinator hackathon.,939,I built the best memory for voice agents while sponsoring @YCombinator hackathon. Introducing: Voice AI + Memory! We built a deep @supermemory integration for @pipecat_ai, so now even your agents have great memory With user profiles, these are almost-instant latency as well :),post,2026-03-05T06:51:50.681Z,103,2026-03-01T02:33:44.419Z,Person,35,0,I built the best memory for voice agents while sponsoring @YCombinator hackathon.<br/><br/>Introducing: Voice AI + Memory!<br/><br/>We built a deep @supermemory integration for @pipecat_ai, so now even your agents have great memory<br/><br/>With user profiles, these are almost-instant latency as well :),20883,131,500,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D10AQHtLHH5Q62XiQ/videocover-high/B4DZynPjXGGwBE-/0/1772332404587?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=xf1-cuQmrN8vhCiywf8Vfx5QSFtTqy29p8bPiYfWWNQ,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQG4Fqwj46yUJw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1725060944740?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=43Shx7EXf5rVeM6VZKEfsHa4lxeU_TfIx4J2jkTMJwk
7434009337557180416,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/dhruv-agarwal99_i-am-going-to-stanford-university-excited-activity-7434009337557180416-Ob6T,I am going to Stanford University!! Excited to say that I am one of the 30 people to be selected to Stanford ASES Summit. Their last program was hosted by Garry Tan, and had Elon Musk, Peter Thiel… | Dhruv Agarwal | 39 comments,https://in.linkedin.com/in/dhruv-agarwal99?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image,dhruv-agarwal99,I am going to Stanford University!!,670,I am going to Stanford University !! Excited to say that I am one of the 30 people to be selected to Stanford ASES Summit. Their last program was hosted by Garry Tan , and had Elon Musk, Peter Thiel and Andrew Ng as Speakers. Eagerly waiting to see who they bring in this time lol,post,2026-03-05T06:51:51.079Z,23,2026-03-01T22:59:03.272Z,Person,39,0,I am going to <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/school/stanford-university/?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Stanford University</a>!!<br/><br/>Excited to say that I am one of the 30 people to be selected to <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/asesstanford?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Stanford ASES</a> Summit. <br/><br/>Their last program was hosted by <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/garrytan?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Garry Tan</a>, and had Elon Musk, Peter Thiel and <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrewyng?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Andrew Ng</a> as Speakers. <br/><br/>Eagerly waiting to see who they bring in this time lol,3603,,500,,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQH6ziD3tNe2tQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/B56Zdte_2cGQ