"https://in.linkedin.com/in/shashank-tiwari-809570252?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Shashank</a> were overjoyed to find we were winners (40k didn&apos;t hurt). Frankly, everyone seated there had fantastic projects, we had a good fortune going <br/>Thank you <a class="link" href="https://in.linkedin.com/in/sachin-teke-314213b3?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Sachin</a> sir, Amal sir and <a class="link" href="https://in.linkedin.com/in/mahesh-shirole-06951431?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Mahesh</a> sir for being awesome and considering me worthy 🙏 .<br/><br/>If you ever see me at a hackathon, please network with me 😊 <br/>Devansh Raulo,2282,,500,,https://static.licdn.com/aero-v1/sc/h/9c8pery4andzj6ohjkjp54ma2
