m and great mentorship.<br/><br/>I have now joined the Apps ML team in Mountain View to work on solving large scale personalization problems for millions of Apps and their contents in Play Store. <br/><br/>Special thanks to:<br/>⭐ <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sima-mofakham-2036b34b?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Sima Mofakham</a> and Mofakham-Mikell Lab  for supporting me through my Master&apos;s and being there like a family.<br/>⭐All my friends and family for all the support and help.<br/><br/>Cheers! 🥂 <br/><br/><a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fgoogle&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#Google</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fsoftwareengineer&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#SoftwareEngineer</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fml&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#ML</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fgraduation&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#Graduation</a>,6348,,500,,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D03AQHrkh300bHKRQ/profile-displayphoto-scale_400_400/B4DZg6HPZnGkAg-/0/1753321634336?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=aNurXjgQru9XIbhKcDqJpP3i6RzH2wsdg52mZYblvh0
7432355773248311296,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/csi---kjsce-student%27s-chapter_ideahackathon-hackathonindia-studentinnovation-activity-7432355773248311296-1XtT,#ideahackathon #hackathonindia #studentinnovation #computersocietyofindia #developersofindia #csi #unionbankofindia | CSI - KJSCE Student's Chapter,https://in.linkedin.com/company/csi---kjsce-student's-chapter?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image,csi---kjsce-student's-chapter,🚨 Most hackathons end at the podium.,89,🚨 Most hackathons end at the podium. iDEA 2.0 ends in a boardroom. After an electrifying first edition, iDEA Hackathon 2.0 is back: bigger, bolder, and now a NATIONAL-LEVEL flagship hackathon in collaboration with Union Bank of India . This isn’t just about winning. It’s about building something that actually goes somewhere. 💰 ₹13 Lakh Prize Pool Not symbolic. Not small. A prize pool that matches the scale of ambition. 💼 Internship Opportunities for Top Teams The journey doesn’t end at results. Top performers unlock real industry exposure and career opportunities. 🌍 GFF Exposure & Bigger Platforms - Global Fintech Fest Selected ideas get the spotlight beyond the hackathon - visibility, mentorship, and pathways to scale your solution further. 📢 Registrations are NOW OPEN. https://ideahackathon.com Form your team. Polish your pitch. Build what matters. 🏆 Because this time, you’re not just coding for a trophy, you’re building for the boardroom. #iDEAHackathon #HackathonIndia #StudentInnovation #ComputerSocietyofIndia #DevelopersOfIndia #CSI #UnionBankofIndia,post,2026-03-05T06:51:52.443Z,0,2026-02-25T09:28:22.763Z,Organization,1,0,🚨 Most hackathons end at the podium.<br/>iDEA 2.0 ends in a boardroom.<br/><br/>After an electrifying first edition, iDEA Hackathon 2.0 is back: bigger, bolder, and now a NATIONAL-LEVEL flagship hackathon in collaboration with <a class="link" href="https://in.linkedin.com/company/unionbankofindia?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Union Bank of India</a>.<br/><br/>This isn’t just about winning.<br/>It’s about building something that actually goes somewhere.<br/><br/>💰 ₹13 Lakh Prize Pool<br/>Not symbolic. Not small.<br/>A prize pool that matches the scale of ambition.<br/><br/>💼 Internship Opportunities for Top Teams<br/>The journey doesn’t end at results.<br/>Top performers unlock real industry exposure and career opportunities.<br/><br/>🌍 GFF Exposure &amp; Bigger Platforms - <a class="link" href="https://in.linkedin.com/company/globalfintechfest?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Global Fintech Fest</a><br/>Selected ideas get the spotlight beyond the hackathon - visibility, mentorship, and pathways to scale your solution further.<br/><br/>📢 Registrations are NOW OPEN.<br/><a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fideahackathon%2Ecom&amp;urlhash=UADR&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" rel="nofollow" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>https://ideahackathon.com</a><br/><br/>Form your team.<br/>Polish your pitch.<br/>Build what matters.<br/><br/>🏆 Because this time, you’re not just coding for a trophy, <br/>you’re building for the boardroom.<br/><br/><a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fideahackathon&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#iDEAHackathon</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fhackathonindia&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#HackathonIndia</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fstudentinnovation&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#StudentInnovation</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fcomputersocietyofindia&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#ComputerSocietyofIndia</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fdevelopersofindia&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#DevelopersOfIndia</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fcsi&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#CSI</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Funionbankofindia&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#UnionBankofIndia</a> ,527,,500,,https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D0BAQEAk4nspIpzsg/company-logo_100_100/B4DZwE_d4EG8AU-/0/1769610272842/csi___kjsce_students_chapter_logo?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=RZbAzzx6X6YRKYijXbGkd_g3bGW8I_kKhJ70FuStHU4
7434834886601035776,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/abhijitmulik_aihackathon-innovation-buildinpublic-activity-7434834886601035776-GMw0,#aihackathon #innovation #buildinpublic #networking #ai #hackathonexperience #learningbybuilding | Abhijit Mulik,https://in.linkedin.com/in/abhijitmulik?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image,abhijitmulik,🚀 AI Hackathon Experience at VJTI – An Incredible 24 Hours of Innovation,58,🚀 AI Hackathon Experience at VJTI – An Incredible 24 Hours of Innovation I recently had the opportunity to participate in the m-Indicator AI Hackathon 2026 held at VJTI, Mumbai. It was a 24-hour non-stop hackathon where teams built AI-driven solutions across various domains. The experience was truly amazing — from brainstorming ideas late into the night, building prototypes under time pressure, to presenting solutions in front of judges. Events like these remind you how powerful collaboration, curiosity, and creativity can be when passionate people come together. One of the highlights for me was meeting Sachin Teke , the founder of m-Indicator. Interacting with him and understanding the vision behind such initiatives was extremely inspiring. What made this hackathon even more special was the community. I met some incredibly talented participants and previous hackathon winners. Their passion, mindset, and attitude toward solving real-world problems were truly motivating. The networking, idea exchanges, and learning from each other were just as valuable as the competition itself. Grateful for the opportunity to be part of such an energetic environment filled with builders, innovators, and problem solvers. Looking forward to participating in many more such events and continuing the journey of building with AI. 🤖✨ #AIHackathon #Innovation #BuildInPublic #Networking #AI #HackathonExperience #LearningByBuilding,post,2026-03-05T06:51:52.512Z,9,2026-03-04T05:39:29.487Z,Person,0,0,🚀 AI Hackathon Experience at VJTI – An Incredible 24 Hours of Innovation<br/><br/>I recently had the opportunity to participate in the m-Indicator AI Hackathon 2026 held at VJTI, Mumbai. It was a 24-hour non-stop hackathon where teams built AI-driven solutions across various domains.<br/><br/>The experience was truly amazing — from brainstorming ideas late into the night, building prototypes under time pressure, to presenting solutions in front of judges. Events like these remind you how powerful collaboration, curiosity, and creativity can be when passionate people come together.<br/><br/>One of the highlights for me was meeting <a class="link" href="https://in.linkedin.com/in/sachin-teke-314213b3?trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>Sachin Teke</a>, the founder of m-Indicator. Interacting with him and understanding the vision behind such initiatives was extremely inspiring.<br/><br/>What made this hackathon even more special was the community. I met some incredibly talented participants and previous hackathon winners. Their passion, mindset, and attitude toward solving real-world problems were truly motivating. The networking, idea exchanges, and learning from each other were just as valuable as the competition itself.<br/><br/>Grateful for the opportunity to be part of such an energetic environment filled with builders, innovators, and problem solvers.<br/><br/>Looking forward to participating in many more such events and continuing the journey of building with AI. 🤖✨<br/><br/><a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Faihackathon&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-tracking-will-navigate>#AIHackathon</a> <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Finnovation&amp;trk=public_post-text" target="_self" data-tracking-control-name="public_post-text" data-track