["https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQEKSglokNbVMw/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56ZxasIxoJQAk-/0/1771048045973?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=Zcfu0j9ViXzAsjkcOzyR73Uz-k_X52mtvBlHWtzQ_SE"],,7428313905539584001,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/stemise_partner-announcement-we-are-excited-to-activity-7428313905539584001-ORCQ,stemise,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/stemise_partner-announcement-we-are-excited-to-activity-7428313905539584001-ORCQ,6,❗ PARTNER ANNOUNCEMENT❗ We are excited to announce our partnership with Cyberwave. Cyberwave Hacks is a student-led hackathon organization that hosts free events, including game jams, where participants can compete for prizes and learn new skills. During this partnership, Cyberwave will be joining us in co-hosting the 2026 STEMEd AI Hackathon (p.s. stay tuned for our posts announcing the event in detail). Thank you, CyberWave Hackathon , for this partnership, and we are very excited!,2026-02-14T05:47:26.479Z,2,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=