,,7429117153812955138,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/dhiraagu_genaihack26-activity-7429117153812955138-7Oju,dhiraagu,["#GenAIHack26"],,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/dhiraagu_genaihack26-activity-7429117153812955138-7Oju,1,Reliving the scenes from Gen AI Hack We had 12 teams of builders come together with one clear mission — build a product and ship it. Over 48 hours, ideas moved beyond discussion and into deployment. Mentor hours were intense, GenAI sessions were practical, and final pitches reflected real execution. This is what GenAI Hack stands for — moving from encouragement to action, from concept to live product. Explore all the products launched during the hackathon: genaihack.io/listings In partnership with SparkHub Co-partner: Synetecs #GenAIHack26,2026-02-16T10:59:15.791Z,0,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=public_post-text","https://fr.linkedin.com/company/mistralai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteratehackathons?trk=public_post-text","https