["https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D22AQGXaPwmQG062w/feedshare-shrink_800/B4DZxXzfTdG8Ag-/0/1770999641648?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=rD8WdQ09-zaSmv07Ceqzd7iIouI5bbUyzcKUAZ21hxY"],,7428502645100695552,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/alainbreillatt_we-are-all-in-on-leveraging-ai-across-the-activity-7428502645100695552-6sPK,alainbreillatt,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/alainbreillatt_we-are-all-in-on-leveraging-ai-across-the-activity-7428502645100695552-6sPK,2,We are all in on leveraging AI across the business at RELEX Solutions and I love seeing notes like this from our less technical team members. For the record we were started by a team of data scientists so our focus on automated decision making has a 20 year heritage across every genre of AI through the decades.,2026-02-14T18:17:25.497Z,0,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=public_post-text","https://fr.linkedin.com/company/mistralai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteratehackathons?trk=public_post-text