,,7431192627418476544,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/felixamoruwa_most-education-tools-talk-at-students-alongside-activity-7431192627418476544-SCCt,felixamoruwa,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/felixamoruwa_most-education-tools-talk-at-students-alongside-activity-7431192627418476544-SCCt,9,Most education tools talk AT students. Alongside 200+ builders at Return of the Agents today, hosted by AI Valley , we hacked and built one that listens, understands context, and talks back WITH them. ElevenLabs transcribes voice. Anthropic 's Claude generates answers with full context. MiniMax Speech-26 speaks it back through multiple voice profiles selected automatically by content type. Technical skill-building shouldn't require anyone to already understand the material before they can ask questions. Thanks AI Valley for hosting a great Hackathon! It was fun building with you Surbhi Bhatnagar !,2026-02-22T04:26:27.259Z,1,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=public_post-text","https://fr.linkedin.com/company/mistralai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteratehackathons?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/school/unsw-founders/?trk=public_post-text"]
["https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E22AQG5_exYkKeseA/feedshare-shrink_1280/B4EZw3ktZjJsAg-/0/1770458896567?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=GkGZSIQn4iKbV3NZnKj98ljuQU1CDptPl7whnzTLBUs"],,7425842834710290433,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/obaid-ur-rahmaan-5bb29814b_hackathon-under-way-engineers-from-around-activity-7425842834710290433-qXU5,obaid-ur-rahmaan-5bb29814b,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/obaid-ur-rahmaan-5bb29814b_hackathon-under-way-engineers-from-around-activity-7425842834710290433-qXU5,19,Hackathon under way! Engineers from around the world just kicked off Nairon's first 24-hour Remote Hackathon! The challenge: Build an AI-powered solution for clinical trial patient matching. People are dying because they don't know trials exist for their condition. Trials are failing because they can't find patients. Massive matching problem. No manual coding allowed. Agents only 🤖 We're evaluating AI nativeness - how well they direct AI tools, not how fast they type. We'll be checking in throughout to see how they think, what questions they ask, and how they iterate. 24 hours. Let's see what they build!,2026-02-07T10:08:17.283Z,0,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=public_post-text","https://fr.linkedin.com/company/mistralai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteratehackathons?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/school/unsw-founders/?trk=public_post-text"]
,["https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQGW6ES-kXDMRQ/video-auto-caption-srt-acs-singleton/B56Zysh1SfJQEk-/0/1772421125440?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=0hMT0RyRWFiMN9fcbhUcjtty9JdoMS0NkhV6AFS96lk"],7434072885650149376,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/jayce-batallones_tired-of-repeating-the-same-tedious-browser-activity-7434072885650149376-_d02,jayce-batallones,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/jayce-batallones_tired-of-repeating-the-same-tedious-browser-activity-7434072885650149376-_d02,164,Tired of repeating the same tedious browser tasks every single day? 😩 Yeah… we were too. So we decided to fix it in just 48 hours. We built Ditto: a smart browser agent that watches your screen recording once → then automates the entire workflow on your machine. No more manual repetition. Just record → relax → repeat and run whenever. Yusuke , Kerui and I (currently in arrayah 's accelerator) just hacked this together at the Mistral Worldwide Hackathon in Sydney. Huge shoutout to the Mistral AI , Iterate , and UNSW Founders for putting on an epic event! If you're curious and want to see Ditto in action, just shoot me a DM as we'd love to give you a quick demo.,2026-03-02T03:11:34.334Z,32,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=public_post-text","https://fr.linkedin.com/company/mistralai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteratehackathons?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/school/unsw-founders/?trk=public_post-text"]
,,7426959250901336064,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/zanmadit_judgai-ai-hackathon-judge-is-an-autonomous-activity-7426959250901336064-BXqL,zanmadit,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/zanmadit_judgai-ai-hackathon-judge-is-an-autonomous-activity-7426959250901336064-BXqL,6,Judgai AI Hackathon Judge is an autonomous system that evaluates hackathon projects the way a real jury would - by analyzing the GitHub repository, demo video, and project claims together. Problem: - The number of participants in hackathons is growing rapidly. - Hackathon projects are becoming increasingly complex. - Manual evaluation is time-consuming and not always objective. - Judges may overlook important files or details of the demonstration. And in general, project reviews can take months - this can help fix that.,2026-02-10T12:04:31.645Z,0,["https://lnkd.in/gSf6bMWY","https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabrinaramonov?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/cyberwave-hackathon?trk=public_post-text","http://genaihack.io/listings","https://mv.linkedin.com/company/sparkhub?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/synetecs?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/genaihack26","https://fi.linkedin.com/company/relexsolutions?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/elevenlabsio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/company/minimax-ai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/aivalleyio?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/in/surbhi-b?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/yusuke-miyashita-79a3771a5?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/in/keruiyang?trk=public_post-text","https://au.linkedin.com/company/live-arrayah?trk=public_post-text","https://fr.linkedin.com/company/mistralai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/iteratehackathons?tr