,,7425104693829218305,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/zero-day-con_ai-driven-attacks-data-is-the-target-activity-7425104693829218305-TM5J,zero-day-con,["#ZDC26","#ZeroDayCon"],,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/zero-day-con_ai-driven-attacks-data-is-the-target-activity-7425104693829218305-TM5J,31,When it comes to nefarious AI, it has one objective. The data. That was the message shared at last year's Zero Day Con by Ronan Murphy , Chief Strategy Officer at Forcepoint , on why data sits at the centre of AI driven attacks. Is data still the primary target, or are attackers starting to chase new commodities? We'll be exploring this and more at #ZDC26 . Join the conversation ➡️ www.zerodaycon.com #ZeroDayCon,2026-02-05T09:15:10.783Z,3,["https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/bloomberg?trk=public_post-text","https://lnkd.in/dS7jMBJ3","https://hk.linkedin.com/in/naman-tandon-83b6566a?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/in/haslinda-amin-0a29892b?trk=public_post-text","https://ie.linkedin.com/company/zero-day-con?trk=public_post-text","https://ie.linkedin.com/in/ronanmurphy1?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/forcepoint?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/zdc26","http://www.zerodaycon.com/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/zerodaycon","https://lnkd.in/dWCiFZ75","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/academicpublishing","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/researchintegrity","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/peerreview","https://cygeniq.ai/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/cygeniq","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/datapoisoning","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aiintegrity","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aigovernance","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/enterpriserisk","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/protectai","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/controlai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/h