["https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D10AQEjzIxp4uWhoQ/image-shrink_1280/B4DZxSeepfIUAg-/0/1770910247883?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=Pf7TkhJTIwuffgA_Wt_coNXYpu0UnAyesVG6KduGE5Q"],,7427735941114564608,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/cygeniq_cygeniq-datapoisoning-aiintegrity-activity-7427735941114564608-n7vb,cygeniq,["#Cygeniq","#DataPoisoning","#AIIntegrity","#AIGovernance","#EnterpriseRisk","#ProtectAI"],,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/cygeniq_cygeniq-datapoisoning-aiintegrity-activity-7427735941114564608-n7vb,10,Data poisoning attacks don’t crash systems. They quietly alter AI behavior over time. For enterprises, this results in biased decisions, compliance exposure, and loss of trust. Cygeniq secures data integrity and governance across the AI lifecycle. https://cygeniq.ai/ #Cygeniq #DataPoisoning #AIIntegrity #AIGovernance #EnterpriseRisk #ProtectAI,2026-02-12T15:30:49.022Z,0,["https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/bloomberg?trk=public_post-text","https://lnkd.in/dS7jMBJ3","https://hk.linkedin.com/in/naman-tandon-83b6566a?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/in/haslinda-amin-0a29892b?trk=public_post-text","https://ie.linkedin.com/company/zero-day-con?trk=public_post-text","https://ie.linkedin.com/in/ronanmurphy1?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/forcepoint?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/zdc26","http://www.zerodaycon.com/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/zerodaycon","https://lnkd.in/dWCiFZ75","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/academicpublishing","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/researchintegrity","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/peerreview","https://cygeniq.ai/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/cygeniq","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/datapoisoning","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aiintegrity","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aigovernance","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/enterpriser