,,7428839087488454656,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/federiconisoli_great-interview-touching-all-the-right-points-activity-7428839087488454656-wV2D,federiconisoli,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/federiconisoli_great-interview-touching-all-the-right-points-activity-7428839087488454656-wV2D,0,Great interview touching all the right points. I have been following ControlAI for a while now and I suggest you do the same (if you care about the future),2026-02-15T16:34:19.613Z,0,["https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/bloomberg?trk=public_post-text","https://lnkd.in/dS7jMBJ3","https://hk.linkedin.com/in/naman-tandon-83b6566a?trk=public_post-text","https://sg.linkedin.com/in/haslinda-amin-0a29892b?trk=public_post-text","https://ie.linkedin.com/company/zero-day-con?trk=public_post-text","https://ie.linkedin.com/in/ronanmurphy1?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/company/forcepoint?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/zdc26","http://www.zerodaycon.com/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/zerodaycon","https://lnkd.in/dWCiFZ75","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/academicpublishing","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/researchintegrity","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/peerreview","https://cygeniq.ai/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/cygeniq","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/datapoisoning","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aiintegrity","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aigovernance","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/enterpriserisk","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/protectai","https://uk.linkedin.com/company/controlai?trk=public_post-text","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/artificialintelligence","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/generativeai","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/llm","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aiinfrastructure","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/aigovernance","https://www.linkedin.c