,,7431743568941322240,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/santosh-sharma-700973249_vfxstudio-animationstudioes-python-activity-7431743568941322240-DXqg,santosh-sharma-700973249,["#vfxstudio","#AnimationStudioes","#python","#nuke","#vfx","#netflix","#warnerbros"],,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/santosh-sharma-700973249_vfxstudio-animationstudioes-python-activity-7431743568941322240-DXqg,16,"Ditching the basic Nuke workflow to implement a robust Studio Pipeline—let’s level up the automation." Just Add These Gizmo Text Format Into " Menu.py " import nuke import shot_loader import importlib def start_welcome_screen(): importlib.reload (shot_loader) shot_loader.show_loader() # Add to Menu with Shortcut 'Alt+W' # Note: 'w' is lowercase for Alt+W. For Ctrl+Shift+W, use 'ctrl+shift+w' nuke.menu ('Nuke').addCommand('File/Project Welcome Loader', 'start_welcome_screen()', 'alt+w') # Optional: Auto-launch on startup nuke.addOnCreate(lambda: start_welcome_screen(), nodeClass='Root') nuke.addOnCreate(lambda: start_welcome_screen(), nodeClass='Root') Thanks Will Move Forward With Auto Write Node--------- Stay Tuned.. Have a Good Day. #vfxstudio #AnimationStudioes #python #nuke #vfx #netflix #warnerbros,2026-02-23T16:55:41.954Z,1,["https://x.com/ma_at_anubis","https://lnkd.in/eZFxzqWa","https://lnkd.in/eYSNmcw9","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/gamedev","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/graphicsprogramming","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/indiedev","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/cpp","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/opengl","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/conceptforge","http://menu.py/","http://importlib.reload/?trk=public_post-text","http://nuke.menu/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/vfxstudio","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/animationstudioes","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/python","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/nuke","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/vfx","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/netflix","https: