,,7424518233032052736,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mishalasad_i-thought-id-share-a-fun-tech-art-project-activity-7424518233032052736-_yDx,mishalasad,,,https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mishalasad_i-thought-id-share-a-fun-tech-art-project-activity-7424518233032052736-_yDx,28,I thought I'd share a fun tech art project that I recently worked on! In this video, I walk through a prototype project‑management tool I built in Python specifically for Houdini artists. The goal is simple: remove the stress of naming conventions, folder structures, and file placement so artists can stay focused on creating. This tool automatically organizes assets, standardizes naming formats, and lays a clean foundation for larger pipeline workflows. It’s simple, expandable, and designed to grow with any production environment, from solo projects to full studio pipelines. Link to project file: https://lnkd.in/euWRjrUa,2026-02-03T18:24:47.633Z,0,["https://x.com/ma_at_anubis","https://lnkd.in/eZFxzqWa","https://lnkd.in/eYSNmcw9","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/gamedev","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/graphicsprogramming","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/indiedev","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/cpp","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/opengl","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/conceptforge","http://menu.py/","http://importlib.reload/?trk=public_post-text","http://nuke.menu/","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/vfxstudio","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/animationstudioes","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/python","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/nuke","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/vfx","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/netflix","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/warnerbros","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/conceptforge","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/gamedev","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/graphicsprogramming","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/python","https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/c","https