Pushing for >15% WoW growth is the only way to find the ceiling—love the focus on Revenue as the single source of truth, Oncel. As a Product Clarity Operator, the biggest risk I see for YC teams hitting these numbers is 'Revenue Noise.' When growth is the only KPI, it’s easy to start building every custom feature request just to keep the 15\\% alive. That’s usually how 'Clarity Rot' sets in and kills A-round momentum. Rooting for the Patientdesk team to keep raising the bar!,https://za.linkedin.com/in/simira-ahmed-a584aa336?trk=public_post_comment_actor-name,simira-ahmed-a584aa336,Simira Ahmed,,2026-02-26T07:06:36.733Z,,0,
