"id: ACoAAEk-ZbcBVPk9fDWpoYTMTnWwdlgwxYWCAls
about: "Hey! I'm Armand! 

I passed my first bill at 18. Spent my youth doing grassroots advocacy for my first-generation immigrant community in Nevada. Became the youngest appointee to sit on government councils advising the Governor on policy decisions that later became law.

Now I'm spending my time building Fed10 to handle the painful parts of government affairs, empowering government affairs teams to spend more time passing legislation!

Check us out: www.fed10.ai"
